To install a single library
    pip install <library required>
    pip install pandas

Command for installing more than one library
    pip install <lib1> <lib2> <lib3>
    pip install pandas scipy

List of libraries needed:
    pandas
    scikit-learn
    matplotlib
    seaborn
    statsmodels
    torch
    tensorflow

pip install -r requirements.txt



